{"tid":1314862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真有乜嘢方法在財政上制裁黑警？","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T11:40:41.000Z","uid":278765,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b067de5c5fe18d7c6ed0528a01a520fa2b270f07","tid":1314862,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"我每年交税，每季都要交差鮈。呢一排個個星期，在媒體上睇住呢班惡狗，借維持秩序為名，發洩佢地情緒為實，將我地D青年人殘害。武力唔夠呢班惡狗鬥，有冇方法，陰乾佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cff4d072bd857af5c34dc54b16de6922807946f","tid":1314862,"uid":50502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"移民 <br />\n<br />\n冇其他方法喇"},{"pid":"ab55ae9a56f0f6e77d7f0025b85e159a50cf45e3","tid":1314862,"uid":258409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"逐仙轉帳交稅？"},{"pid":"fa3767fe8b8420555b8e666cc27e33ed63c412e0","tid":1314862,"uid":181097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a42fde4b84b0655de6d637f59b425dbb0c8cfb24","tid":1314862,"uid":48889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"冇 政府只會KEEP住加呢班黑警人工 令佢地愈黎愈狗"},{"pid":"aeb23fa6ae6b8d5f3c6fcd42e2546bf44c60d3e2","tid":1314862,"uid":4739,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:17:14.000Z","msg":"一齊唔做狗生意"},{"pid":"e6fc928ead96193641077e2373a7e06f890368f4","tid":1314862,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"當做到敵在明你在暗時"},{"pid":"3005c010c06e611e450ef49e64c8c6038cfbc973","tid":1314862,"uid":278765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"可惜我唔係警總飯堂經理，否則我老虎蟹唔辭職，日日幫班惡狗添加營養！"},{"pid":"8d7fbe399c93e65eb231c17a48f594ce8b0be02c","tid":1314862,"uid":196671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"其實都好難。睇返19-20年預算案，正苦財政收入來源主要係利得稅（1,600億）、賣地收入（1,400億）、印花稅（760億），薪俸稅只係排第四（666億），而差餉只得199億。除非可以令到企業、買樓人士、證券公司唔交稅，以及地產商唔投地，否則好難令到正苦冇錢撥俾黑警。更何況即使全社會抵制正苦，佢仍然有大量財政儲備繼續維持運作同送錢俾差佬。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/io.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fio.html&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPan%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=07caec1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/io.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/1819issf04-major-sources-of-government-revenue-20190304-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fresearch-publications%2Fchinese%2F1819issf04-major-sources-of-government-revenue-20190304-c.pdf&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPan%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=07308706\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/1819issf04-major-sources-of-government-revenue-20190304-c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"1101274562ed96397320d46d0433c9555f65f3f6","tid":1314862,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"可惜我唔係做財仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}